Don't try with fakes--

411
00:23:03,315 --> 00:23:04,883
NARUTO (VOICEOVER):
Here I am, back

412
00:23:04,918 --> 00:23:08,276
from defeating Zabuza,
ready to really kick butt.

413
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:09,312
