414
00:23:09,345 --> 00:23:11,982
More training, more
tests, more exams.

415
00:23:12,016 --> 00:23:13,819
How long are they
going to keep us here?

416
00:23:13,852 --> 00:23:17,057
It's like we're in daycare.

417
00:23:17,090 --> 00:23:18,960
Man, don't they
understand there are

418
00:23:18,993 --> 00:23:22,032
a lot of other dangerous
ninja like Zabuza out there?

